cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SD 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.AI - The paper deals with reinforcement learning techniques and their application to a specific task, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
2. cs.CL - The paper uses natural language commands to guide the reinforcement learning agent, which involves natural language processing techniques. 
3. cs.LG - The paper proposes a novel technique for improving the performance of reinforcement learning agents, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.RO - The paper deals with the application of reinforcement learning techniques to a real-time strategy game, which falls under the domain of robotics. 
5. cs.SD - The paper proposes a technique for improving the performance of reinforcement learning agents through the use of natural language commands, which falls under the domain of software development.
